# 🧩 Day 35 – Prompt Puzzle: Master AI Prompting Through Play

## 📌 Project
Prompt Puzzle is an interactive educational game that teaches Prompt Engineering through hands-on challenges. Instead of reading theory, users learn by building, cleaning, and optimizing prompts while receiving instant feedback and performance analysis.

---

## 🚀 Features

- Single-file HTML application
- Fully Offline
- Pure HTML, CSS & JavaScript
- Premium Dark UI
- Responsive Design
- Drag & Drop Prompt Builder
- Click-to-Place Fallback
- 6 Randomized Prompt Scenarios
- Three Interactive Challenge Types
- Live Performance Tracking
- Prompt Performance Report
- Prompt DNA Visualization
- Personalized AI Feedback
- Replay with Randomized Scenario Order

---

## 🎯 Challenge Types

### 1. Build the Prompt
Arrange prompt blocks in the correct order.

### 2. Clean the Prompt
Remove unnecessary prompt blocks and optimize the prompt.

### 3. Choose the Best Prompt
Compare multiple prompts and identify the most effective one.

---

## 📊 Performance Metrics

- Accuracy
- Time Taken
- Moves
- Wrong Placements
- Hints Used
- Optimization Bonus
- Final Prompt Score
- Rank (S–D)
- Prompt DNA Analysis

